classes.description: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.

icon.description: The icon to display in the SpeedDial Floating Action Button.

openIcon.description: The icon to display in the SpeedDial Floating Action Button when the SpeedDial is open.

descriptions.root: Styles applied to the root element.
descriptions.icon: Styles applied to the icon component.
descriptions.iconOpen: Styles applied to the icon component if `open={true}`.
descriptions.iconWithOpenIconOpen: Styles applied to the icon when an `openIcon` is provided and if `open={true}`.
descriptions.openIcon: Styles applied to the `openIcon` if provided.
descriptions.openIconOpen: Styles applied to the `openIcon` if provided and if `open={true}`.
